title: Friends without Benefits ( DJ D- Nice Interview)
itunes:title: Friends without Benefits ( DJ D- Nice Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had friend to the room DJ DNice stop by where he spoke about the evolution of Club Quarantine, The Future Of DJs, New Music and more. Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Rick Santorum while also giving him a quick history lesson on AmeriKKKa. Lastly they opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners agree or disagree with Steve Harvey comments about men and females being platonic friends.
